# bootstrap.d/vars/globals.env -- Subproject global defaults
# Sourced automatically by bootstrap.d/lib/defaults.sh after task defaults,
# so values here override task-level defaults.

# -- BSS_GLB_TAGS: active tag filter (empty = run all tasks)
#
# Each task declares its own BSS_<TASK>_TAG in vars/default.env.
# If BSS_GLB_TAGS is non-empty, only tasks whose tag is in this list run.
#
# Override at invocation (space-separated string):
#   BSS_GLB_TAGS="install" make bootstrap
#   BSS_GLB_TAGS="install configure" make bootstrap
#
# shellcheck disable=SC2206  # intentional word-split from env string
BSS_GLB_TAGS=(${BSS_GLB_TAGS:-})

# BSS_GLB_ENVIRONMENT="production"
